result.execSummary:
The defendant Timothy K Klanderman was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Timothy K Klanderman is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Timothy K Klanderman was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct, a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
